metadata.name: lil Lol
metadata.description:
little lol, that's what I called Veronica when I was shooting..

"In the age range between nine and fourteen there are girls who, for some enchanted wanderers twice or many times their age, reveal their true essence-an essence not human, but nymphic (i.e. demonic); 
and these little chosen ones I propose to call thus: nymphetki."

Vladimir Nabokov "Lolita"
